Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(All of us) us, us{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:31.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(All of us) a-su, a-su{\i}
