Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.97,0:01:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Straw Hats were looking for Vegapunk,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.85,0:01:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but were cornered\Nby some unknown operative's trickery.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.06,0:01:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The video feeds...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...are going off one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone else is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:01:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...in the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.99,0:01:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.42,0:02:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.26,0:02:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not listening to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.10,0:02:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.10,0:02:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a really troubling situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What if the communication failure...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...and this situation of\Nbeing trapped in the barrier...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.74,0:02:40.91,On Top,,0,0,0,,GOOD
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...were all calculated?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That means somebody...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.41,0:02:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...wants to kill us all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Stella!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.87,0:02:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.21,0:02:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did this to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:03:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The hands of evil closed in\Non Shaka who found Vegapunk.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that you're okay!\NI'll unlock the door now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaka... Who are you here with?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.27,0:03:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Second Ohara!\NThe Mastermind's Ambition!"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.95,0:04:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting quite cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How much longer will it take?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.62,0:04:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll soon arrive at Egghead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.96,0:04:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should get some food.\NLet the Vice Admirals know, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.64,0:04:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.64,0:04:35.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,JUSTICE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.89,0:04:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He is about to have a meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:53.96,On Top,,0,0,0,,ST. JAYGARCIA SATURN OF THE ELDERS
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your guard up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:08.47,On Top,,0,0,0,,FUTURE ISLAND EGGHEAD
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:11.93,On Top,,0,0,0,,LABORATORY, FUTURE ISLAND EGGHEAD
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.06,0:05:13.60,On Top,,0,0,0,,BUILDING C, A, B
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:17.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,LABORATORY, 2ND FLOOR, BUILDING B
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?! Uncle Kizaru?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He is on his way here with a fleet of\Nover a hundred vessels, large and small.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Over a hundred?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,CP-0's mission is to kill Doctor\Nand wait for Kizaru's arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,0:05:36.92,On Top,,0,0,0,,FABIRIOPHASE FACTORY
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They're sending a Navy Admiral...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The Government's stance\Nis out of the ordinary...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, they must be taking the situation\Nmore seriously than they did with Ohara.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.17,0:05:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Reason one. Doctor has inherited\NOhara's forbidden research,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and is making progress with it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.30,0:05:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Reason two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.47,0:05:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Egghead has battle capabilities\Nwhich Ohara didn't have!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You mean the Seraphim\Nand all of the Pacifistas?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, those are good enough reasons\Nfor enormous forces to be deployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Contact me when anything happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All communication devices in the Labophase\Nare inoperative.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Got it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Learn from history\Nwhat the Navy is gonna do here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.54,0:06:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we, and this research facility,\Ngoing to suffer the same fate as Ohara?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.76,0:06:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! There's no time to think!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get off of Egghead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the ship ready!\NWe'll leave the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Before the Navy gets here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as Sentomaru-{\i1}san{\i} told us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay... There is no turning back now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you going to settle this?\NOld Man Punk...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp! Lilith!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:47.67,On Top,,0,0,0,,LABORATORY, 3RD FLOOR, BUILDING C
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You shitty brat! Unpetrify me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I lowered my guard on my right side,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but I still got my left side!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want a taste of my Weapons Left?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you surrender now,\Nmaybe I'll forgive...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll shoot you if you don't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! S-Snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose...\NWhose orders are you working under?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.29,0:08:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Pythagoras!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.81,0:08:50.61,On Top,,0,0,0,,LABORATORY, 2ND FLOOR, BUILDING A
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if everyone's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been hearing huge explosions\Nand screams.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:09:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that the Seraphim are rampaging.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's incomprehensible!\NI thought the Seraphim were on our side...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.13,0:09:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps someone\Noverrode the command again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone inside the lab...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about Nami and the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a person who instantly rushes to her\Nwhen he hears her scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Teams in combat can't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,While everyone's fighting, there's the risk of\Nsomething happening to Vegapunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We should continue searching.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.79,0:09:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Let's find him ASAP!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there is a room\Nthat was once used and is now sealed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.04,0:09:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think\Nanyone would go there though...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.51,0:09:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go check.\NMaybe we'll find some trace of a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Show us the way, Atlas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:10.86,On Top,,0,0,0,,LABORATORY, 3RD FLOOR, BUILDING A
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Little Jinbe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if you're\Nthe pinnacle of science or whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you even touch Nami-{\i1}san{\i}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Edison, stay with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Edison!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-{\i1}san{\i}! I'll lighten myself up\Nand go find Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji-{\i1}san{\i}! You're awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Little Jinbe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know... the power of love?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...Red Hawk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.84,0:12:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! The flames on their backs\Nhaven't gone out yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They're quite tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,When the flames on their backs go out,\Nthat's the only chance that our attacks will work,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's only for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how fast they switch\Nfrom offense to defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! While we were focused on their flames,\Nthe Hawkeye look-alike is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They must've changed\Ntheir target priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.95,0:12:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll save the troublesome ones for later\Nand eliminate the weak ones first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, they could also upset\Nthe tough ones by killing their friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so aggravating!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is exactly the kind of ruthless tactic that\Ninhumane bastards like them would come up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy, leave him to me! I'll chase him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.14,0:12:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Usopp! Go with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He can get lost easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so high-maintenance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.31,0:13:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Roronoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you call me "Usopp"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're fighting me right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...Hawk Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Go out, fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool. Wait, Straw Hat! Think!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never beat him that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:14:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is everything that happened\Nthe day before the famous Egghead Incident.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.34,0:14:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it all started three months earlier.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:18.52,On Top,,0,0,0,,SACRED MARIJOA, THREE MONTHS AGO
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:37.04,On Top,,0,0,0,,SACRED MARIJOA, THREE MONTHS AGO
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sacred Marijoa, three months ago.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...is... ...g... ...d...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is E... ...d...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is Egghe... ...d...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to talk to... ...igher-ups.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want from them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...need to talk to the higher-ups...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:14:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I said "What do you want?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dr. Vegapunk is...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...researching the 100-Year Void.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Upon receiving that tip,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}CP5 was dispatched to Egghead\Nto verify the truth,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but found no evidence.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After completing the investigation, the ship\Nmysteriously disappeared on its way back.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To investigate the disappearance,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}first CP7, then CP8 headed to Egghead,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but no one returned to the Government.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.70,0:15:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is Egghead...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:16:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Put me through to the higher-ups...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Later, there was a meeting\Nbetween the Five Elders and another figure,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the betrayal of the genius scientist\Nresearching the 100-Year Void...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...became clear.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Five Elders decided on\NDr. Vegapunk's assassination.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cipher Pol "Aigis" Zero,\Ntasked with that mission, set sail.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, one of the Five Elders\Ndecided to go in person,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}in anticipation of\NVegapunk's counterattack.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He assigned Admiral Kizaru as his escort.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In addition, reinforcements were requested\Nto various Navy branches.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The deployment was on the scale of a war.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, another ship came calling...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That of the Emperor of the Sea,\NStraw Hat Luffy.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Government was not content\Nwith the unexpected intruders' landing.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.86,0:17:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,See?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Things are getting complicated again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's them again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In any case, the incident will come to an end\Nthe next day,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the outcome will shock the world\Nin an unexpected way.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:24.02,On Top,,0,0,0,,OLD DEVIL FRUIT RESEARCH LABORATORY\NUNDERGROUND
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.34,0:18:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this all your doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Why did you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,York!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Stella!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.70,0:19:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to become a Celestial Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.79,0:19:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, York?!\NYou've been to Marijoa, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to be as filthy as they are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something Shaka would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's dead now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's confusing. We're all Vegapunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't one Dr. Vegapunk be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:20:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...enough in this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far I have run{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:21.22,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doredake hashitte kita noka{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without knowing it, I counted scars{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:28.51,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}wakaranai mama kizuato kazoeta{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A treasure map in my head all along{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:35.94,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}zutto atama no naka ni aru takara no chizu{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still looking for the future{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:42.45,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mirai wo sagashi tsuzuketeru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The real promise{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:49.16,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hontou no yakusoku wa{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lies much deeper in my heart{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:56.33,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mune no oku no motto oku ni aru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:21:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A dream that no one can catch up with{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:21:05.47,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}dare mo mina oitsukenai yume{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.51,0:21:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's all I hold on to{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.51,0:21:11.18,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitotsu dakishimete{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To you who smiles like the sun{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:18.27,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}taiyou no youni warau anata e{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll sing the same song as that day{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:25.20,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ano hi to onaji uta wo utau yo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This wish I don't want to forget even when I grow up{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:32.24,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}otona ni nattemo wasuretakunai{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until it reaches you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:39.71,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kono negai ga todoku made{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.59,0:21:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Dive into the Sea of Information!\NThe Punk Records Library!"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.47,0:21:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, I'm Lilith, one of the Satellites of\NDr. Vegapunk, the genius scientist!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:22:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Edison, also Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.02,0:22:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we'll introduce this one! Sakazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.78,0:22:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He is the Admiral of the Fleet for the Navy\Nand a Logia type Mag-Mag Fruit user.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.70,0:22:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He can turn his body into magma\Nand manipulate it at will!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.04,0:22:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He was born on August 16th\Nand likes white rice and hot pepper!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.87,0:22:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakazuki believes in thorough justice,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.71,0:22:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and during the Buster Call at Ohara, he even\Nsank a refugee ship full of ordinary islanders.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.30,0:22:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In the Paramount War,\Nhe beat pirate after pirate...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.80,0:22:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...as one of the Navy's greatest powers,\Nthe Three Admirals.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.64,0:22:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He eventually pierced Ace's belly\Nwith magma, taking his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.73,0:22:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you're a Navy soldier,\Nyou can't forgive those thugs, the pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.03,0:22:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, he fought Kuzan for the position of\Nthe Admiral of the Fleet after Sengoku had retired.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.45,0:22:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,After a fierce battle, Sakazuki won\Nand became the new Admiral of the Fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.29,0:23:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a rugged face and personality.\NHe is always hostile to the Straw Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll continue to be a major threat\Nto Luffy and his team.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.13,0:23:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.97,0:23:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've seen it,\Ndonate to our research fund!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.51,0:23:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,See you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.77,0:23:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Emperor Red-Haired\Ncontinues to reign over the seas!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.98,0:23:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fearlessly confronting him is a man{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.98,0:23:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with a bounty of 3 billion berries\Nfrom the Worst Generation!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.11,0:23:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Both holding fast to their beliefs,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.95,0:23:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the two captains in a deep historical rivalry\Nface off in distant Elbaph!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.08,0:23:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"Clash! Shanks vs. Eustass Kid"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.83,0:23:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
